    },
    {
      "scene_index": 4,
      "label": "第四场",
      "characters_present": [
        "刘世昌",
        "刘升",
        "初次相逢承恩爱",
        "明日里定要多谢拜",
        "赵大",
        "赵妻"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘世昌、刘升同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘世昌",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "急急忙忙往前奔，"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘世昌",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "不觉来到一窑门。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘世昌",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来此窑门，刘升上前言道，你我在此借宿一宵，明日早行。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘升",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这我会。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘升",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我说有人么，走出一个来！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵大上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵大",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是谁呀？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘升",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我们要到你们这来睡觉啦！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵大",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你这小子，满嘴胡说八道！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘升",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "什么小子？你才是小子呐！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘世昌",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，大哥请了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵大",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请啦，你们是干什么的？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘世昌",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我乃行路之人，天降大雨，无有旅店，欲想在大哥处，借宿一宵，明日早行。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵大",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这才是会说话的呐。这个不要紧，请到窑里坐吧。我与你牵着马。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘世昌",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这就不敢，请。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵大",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你看你们的衣裳，都淋湿啦，快脱下来，我与你晾晾吧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘世昌",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有劳了。请问大哥尊姓大名？"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵大",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在下，姓赵，哥儿一个，人都叫我赵老大。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘世昌",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "原来是赵大哥。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵大",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请问客人尊姓吓？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘世昌",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "卑人刘世昌，乃四川华阳县人氏。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵大",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "但不知作何买卖？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘世昌",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贩卖绸缎为生。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵大",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "原来是大买卖。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘世昌",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小本钱。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵大",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好说好说。我说你们还没有吃饭吧？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘世昌",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这……前途用过了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵大",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得啦，得啦，哪用过？咱们都不是外人，我也没有什么好吃的，也不过粗菜粗"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵大",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "饭而已，等我与你烫酒去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘世昌",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有劳了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵大",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "慢着，我看这位客人，他行李里头，沉甸甸的，八成银子不少。我想我烧窑一"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵大",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "辈子，也发不了财，不免将他害死，这银子都是我的啦。就是这个主意，老婆"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵大",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵妻上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵妻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来了来了。当家的什么事？"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵大",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老婆，咱们要发财！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵妻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "发什么财？"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵大",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "刚才来了二位客人，是一主一仆，乃是卖绸缎的大客商，他行李里头，全是银"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵大",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "子，我想把他害了，这银子都是咱们的啦！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵妻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "害人我可不会呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵大",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "别嚷，别嚷！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵妻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你说害人，怎么个害法吓？"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵大",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他们没有吃饭呐，你与他安排点酒饭，我把酒里头，与他下上点耗子药，他们"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵大",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吃了，不到一个时辰，管保他就跷缏子。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵妻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这个，我倒能办得了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵妻下。赵妻托盘子上，下毒药，赵妻下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵大",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "酒钣到啦，二位请用吧。来来来，我与你们斟上！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘世昌",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有劳了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘世昌",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "好一个赵大哥多慷慨，"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘世昌",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "一霎时酒饭摆上来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘世昌",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "借宿一霄理不该。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘世昌",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "昏昏沉沉倒卧在土台。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘世昌",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "初次相逢承恩爱"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘世昌",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "明日里定要多谢拜"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵大",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "看他二人已经醉啦，待我将门倒锁上，咱们明个见。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵大下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘世昌",
          "line_type": "西皮导板",
          "musical_style": "西皮导板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "时才朦胧将睡倒，"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘世昌",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "一霎时心中似火烧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘世昌",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "中了赵大计笼牢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘世昌",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "奴才一命赴阴曹。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘世昌",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "爹娘吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘世昌",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "一命定然赴阴曹！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘世昌死。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘升",
          "line_type": "西皮导板",
          "musical_style": "西皮导板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "时才间醉酒将合眼，"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘升",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我心中好似刀来穿。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘升",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "中了他娘的巧机关！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘升",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我的妈妈呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘升死。赵大、赵妻同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵大",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "天亮了，咱们去看看。没有什么动静，光景是死啦。待我开开门，"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵大",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "喝，两人死了一对。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵妻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这两个死尸怎么办呐，抬出去埋了吧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵大",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不好，不好，倘若被人看见，那不是白做了活儿啦吗？有啦，有啦，咱们把他"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵大",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二人尸首，剁成肉酱，和在泥里，烧成了盆子，就是神仙也不能找寻着！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵妻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好，等我拿刀去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵大",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来，咱们动手吧！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵妻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "当家的，你看画上那个判官，他拿两个眼睛瞪我。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵大",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他瞪你，待我把他的眼睛与他剜了去！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵大剜判官眼。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵大",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得啦，咱们这可发财啦，赶紧叫泥瓦匠，先盖起房子来再说！正是："
        },
        {
          "character": "赵大",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "禹门三激浪，平地一声雷。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵大、赵妻同下。）"
        }
      ],
